# **9. Styling (Tailwind Recommended)**

Install:

```
pnpm add -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
pnpm tailwindcss init -p
```

Add to `globals.css`:

```css
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
```

